    'topic.risk_thinking': 'Risk-Based Thinking',
    'start.how_content': '<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px 20px;line-height:1.9;"><div>🔍 <strong style="color:var(--text);">Examine hotspots</strong> in each area to find clues and collect items</div><div>🎒 <strong style="color:var(--text);">Select an item</strong> from your inventory, then click a hotspot to use it</div><div>🧩 <strong style="color:var(--text);">Solve puzzles</strong> — every answer is grounded in real quality principles</div><div>📋 <strong style="color:var(--text);">Check Field Notes</strong> — clues and facts are recorded automatically</div><div>💬 <strong style="color:var(--text);">Use Group Chat</strong> — coordinate with your team in real time</div><div>🔑 <strong style="color:var(--text);">Confirm codes together</strong> — key milestones require all members to enter the code</div></div><div style="margin-top:10px;padding:8px 12px;background:rgba(0,153,230,0.07);border-left:3px solid var(--accent);border-radius:2px;font-size:0.77rem;color:var(--dim);line-height:1.7;">There are <strong style="color:var(--text);">5 areas</strong> and <strong style="color:var(--text);">11 puzzles</strong> to complete in <strong style="color:var(--text);">25 minutes</strong>. Areas unlock as you progress — you cannot skip ahead.</div>',
    'start.rules_content': '<table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;"><tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);"><td style="padding:7px 8px 7px 0;width:28px;font-size:1rem;">👥</td><td style="padding:7px 0;color:var(--dim);"><strong style="color:var(--text);">Team size:</strong> 3 – 5 members. All must be connected before the game starts.</td></tr><tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);"><td style="padding:7px 8px 7px 0;font-size:1rem;">⏱️</td><td style="padding:7px 0;color:var(--dim);"><strong style="color:var(--text);">Simultaneous start:</strong> Every player must click <em>"I\'m Ready"</em>. The timer starts for all at the same moment.</td></tr><tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);"><td style="padding:7px 8px 7px 0;font-size:1rem;">🔑</td><td style="padding:7px 0;color:var(--dim);"><strong style="color:var(--text);">Team confirmation:</strong> At key checkpoints the code is revealed to all — every member must type it to proceed.</td></tr><tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);"><td style="padding:7px 8px 7px 0;font-size:1rem;">🚪</td><td style="padding:7px 0;color:var(--dim);"><strong style="color:var(--text);">Area locks:</strong> Each area is locked until the previous task is completed — complete tasks in order.</td></tr><tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);"><td style="padding:7px 8px 7px 0;font-size:1rem;">❌</td><td style="padding:7px 0;color:var(--dim);"><strong style="color:var(--text);">Wrong answers:</strong> Each incorrect answer deducts <strong style="color:var(--danger);">10 points</strong> from your final score — think before you submit.</td></tr><tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);"><td style="padding:7px 8px 7px 0;font-size:1rem;">💡</td><td style="padding:7px 0;color:var(--dim);"><strong style="color:var(--text);">Hints:</strong> Each area has one hint available. Using a hint costs <strong style="color:var(--danger);">−60 seconds</strong> and <strong style="color:var(--danger);">−50 points</strong>. Hints are subtle — they do not give you the answer.</td></tr><tr style=""><td style="padding:7px 8px 7px 0;font-size:1rem;">🏁</td><td style="padding:7px 0;color:var(--dim);"><strong style="color:var(--text);">One attempt:</strong> Each group plays once. Results are final and posted to the leaderboard.</td></tr></table>',
    'start.scoring_content': '<table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:10px;"><thead><tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);"><th style="text-align:left;font-size:0.65rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px;color:var(--dim);padding:5px 0;">What</th><th style="text-align:right;font-size:0.65rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px;color:var(--dim);padding:5px 0;">Points</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #14162a;"><td style="padding:8px 0;color:var(--dim);">✅ Each puzzle solved</td><td style="padding:8px 0;text-align:right;color:var(--accent2);font-weight:bold;">+200 pts</td></tr><tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #14162a;"><td style="padding:8px 0;color:var(--dim);">⏱️ Every second remaining on the clock <em>(win only)</em></td><td style="padding:8px 0;text-align:right;color:var(--accent2);font-weight:bold;">+2 pts / sec</td></tr><tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #14162a;"><td style="padding:8px 0;color:var(--dim);">❌ Each wrong answer</td><td style="padding:8px 0;text-align:right;color:var(--danger);font-weight:bold;">−10 pts</td></tr><tr style=""><td style="padding:8px 0;color:var(--dim);">💡 Using a hint</td><td style="padding:8px 0;text-align:right;color:var(--danger);font-weight:bold;">−50 pts &amp; −60s</td></tr></tbody></table><div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:6px;"><div style="background:#0a0c18;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:10px 14px;text-align:center;"><div style="font-size:0.65rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px;color:var(--dim);margin-bottom:4px;">Max puzzle pts</div><div style="font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:bold;color:var(--accent2);">2,200</div><div style="font-size:0.68rem;color:var(--dim);">11 × 200</div></div><div style="background:#0a0c18;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:10px 14px;text-align:center;"><div style="font-size:0.65rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px;color:var(--dim);margin-bottom:4px;">Max time bonus</div><div style="font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:bold;color:var(--accent2);">3,000</div><div style="font-size:0.68rem;color:var(--dim);">1,500 sec × 2</div></div></div><div style="margin-top:8px;padding:8px 12px;background:rgba(255,215,0,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,215,0,0.25);border-radius:4px;text-align:center;font-size:0.78rem;color:#ffd700;">🏆 Maximum possible score: <strong>5,200 pts</strong> — all puzzles solved, no wrong answers, no hints, instant finish</div>',
